Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:01.81,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}交わした約束忘れないよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:04.16,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}目を閉じ確かめる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:09.67,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}押し寄せた闇ふり払って進むよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:25.70,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}いつになったら失くした未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:31.84,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}私ここでまた見ること出来るの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:36.57,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}溢れ出したふまの影を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:42.08,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}何度でも裂いてこの世界歩んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:47.77,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}止めどなく刻まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:53.26,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}時は今始まり告げ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.36,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}変わらない思いをのせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:03.84,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}閉ざされた扉開けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.19,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}目覚めたココロは走り出した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.63,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}未来を描くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:14.82,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}難しい道で立ち止まっても空は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:19.61,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}綺麗な青さでいつも待っててくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.77,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}だからこわくない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.82,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}もう何があっても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.55,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}くじけない
Comment: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:01.81,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为了不忘记交换过的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:04.16,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}而闭上眼睛再次确定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:09.67,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}驱散汇集的黑暗继续前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:25.70,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}要到什么时候 失去的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:31.84,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我才能在这里再次眺望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:36.57,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无数次撕裂漫溢的无法磨灭的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:42.08,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}在这世界上不断前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:47.77,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}打上无尽的刻印的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:53.26,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}时间此刻宣告着开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.36,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}乘载着不变的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:03.84,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}去打开闭锁的心扉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:09.63,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}苏醒的心为了描绘未来而奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:14.82,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}即使在泥泞的路上停滞不前天空也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:19.61,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}带着美丽的蔚蓝一直等待着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.77,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}所以不必害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.82,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:27.55,opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}也不会气馁
Comment: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.50,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}錆び付いた心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.50,0:24:24.43,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}音もない世界 何を見てるの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:29.11,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}またねを言える顔を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:31.89,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}それを繰り返すだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:34.55,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}気付けばそこには
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.69,0:24:39.09,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}ひとりきりで泣く後ろ姿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:40.68,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}辛いような
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.78,0:24:43.32,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}寂しいような 場所
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:47.45,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}手を繋いでいたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:51.35,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}何度でも名前を呼ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.56,0:24:55.04,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}不確かな未来でも
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.17,0:25:02.88,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}離せないもの 思うだけ心が痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.00,0:25:04.77,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}ここにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.89,0:25:06.61,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}ここにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.76,0:25:12.12,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}帰る場所はここだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.33,0:25:14.92,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}いつだって変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.08,0:25:20.99,ed3jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an9}思いを残すの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.50,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}锈蚀老化的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.50,0:24:24.43,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}在没有声音的世界里  你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:29.11,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}寻找着可以道别的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:31.89,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}仅仅如此地周而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:34.55,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}转眼一看  那里就是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.69,0:24:39.09,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}孤身一人的哭泣背影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.13,0:24:40.68,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}辛酸痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.78,0:24:43.32,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}而又寂寞难耐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.58,0:24:47.45,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}好想牵住你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.63,0:24:51.35,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}无论几次我都会呼喊你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.56,0:24:55.04,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}即使未来无法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.17,0:25:02.88,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}无法割舍的东西  只要想到就会心如刀绞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.00,0:25:04.77,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.89,0:25:06.61,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.76,0:25:12.12,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}但是哪儿才是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.33,0:25:14.92,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}无论多久都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.08,0:25:20.99,ed3cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur7\an3}就留在记忆中吧
